dct_title_s: Horta and Pim Bays ; Fayal Channel
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures, soundings, and spot heights. Includes 4 cross sections: Town of Horta from the anchorage; Magdalena Rocks; The channel of Fayal from the south-westward; The channel of Fayal from the northward. "Sold by R.B. Bate, agent for the Admiralty charts, 21 Poultry." "1940." Historic Maps copy has paper label on verso: No. 1940.
dct_creator_sm: Vidal, A. T. E. (Alexander Thomas Emeric), 1792-1863
dct_publisher_sm: London : Published according to Act of Parliament at the Hydrographic Office of the Admiralty, July 5th 1849.
